  <title>Integrons in Xanthomonas: A source of species genome diversity</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=50314126b064dfbc8f8273706c8f6f8a&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
